description:
The statue of Bio Guera is located on the roundabout of the Cardinal Bernardin Gantin International Airport in Cadjehoun (AICBG);

The statue is composed of a cast iron shell (T3 copper) with an average thickness of 5 mm mounted on a steel structure; the whole resting on a reinforced concrete foundation;

The total height of the monument is 10 m, including 10 m in length, 3 m in width, and 7 m in height for the statue itself.
